      • start

        public boolean start(String fullPath,
                     String sequence)
        Description copied from class: Player
        Starts off the player, loading a specific project if specified. This method is defined in the RunnableComponent interface.
        Specified by:
        start in interface RunnableComponent
        Overrides:
        start in class Player
        Parameters:
        fullPath - Full path to the JClic project file to be loaded. Can be null.
        sequence - Optional parameter, used only when fullPath is not null. It indicates the sequence where the to start. It's also possible to indicate a string representation of a number "N". In this case, the player will start with the activity indicated by the Nth element of the main sequence of the project.
        Returns:
        true if the player starts successfully. false otherwise.
